<p>这是我绘制的第一个图形. 以后将会用python绘制很多图.</p>

<p>解析:</p>



<pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-python hljs "> <span class="hljs-comment">#PythonDraw.py</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> turtle
turtle.setup(<span class="hljs-number">650</span>, <span class="hljs-number">350</span>, <span class="hljs-number">200</span>, <span class="hljs-number">200</span>)
turtle.penup()
turtle.fd(-<span class="hljs-number">250</span>)
turtle.pendown()
turtle.pensize(<span class="hljs-number">25</span>)
turtle.pencolor(<span class="hljs-string">'purple'</span>)
turtle.seth(-<span class="hljs-number">40</span>)
<span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> range(<span class="hljs-number">4</span>):
    turtle.circle(<span class="hljs-number">40</span>, <span class="hljs-number">80</span>)
    turtle.circle(-<span class="hljs-number">40</span>, <span class="hljs-number">80</span>)
turtle.circle(<span class="hljs-number">40</span>, <span class="hljs-number">80</span>/<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)
turtle.fd(<span class="hljs-number">40</span>)
turtle.circle(<span class="hljs-number">16</span>, <span class="hljs-number">180</span>)
turtle.fd(<span class="hljs-number">40</span>*<span class="hljs-number">2</span>/<span class="hljs-number">3</span>)
turtle.done()</code></pre>

<p>setup()函数</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>建立一个窗口, 它有四个参数, 分别是 <br>
  窗口的长, 宽(高), 窗口左上角起始位置x, y <br>
  不给出3,4个参数默认窗口在正中央.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>penup()函数</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>将画笔抬起的函数,这种情况下,画笔移动不会有痕迹</p>
</blockquote>

<p>pendown()函数</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>将画笔落下的函数,画笔落下了,移动就会制图了</p>
</blockquote>

<p>pensize()函数</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>画笔大小的函数</p>
</blockquote>

<p>pencolor()函数</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>设置画笔颜色的函数</p>
</blockquote>

<p>forward()函数</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>向前移动函数, 别名为<em>fd()</em></p>
</blockquote>

<p>goto()函数</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>将画笔移动到坐标位置函数</p>
</blockquote>

<p>circle()函数</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>第一个参数为半径, 第二个参数为角度 <br>
  如果不给第二个参数, 默认画一个半径为第一个参数的圆 <br>
  角度正为逆时针, 角度负为顺时针</p>
</blockquote>

<p>done()函数</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>让窗口停下来的函数(不会闪退)</p>
</blockquote>

